body:
This internal cleanup removes the hand-coded node-to-node pointers in the AstNode structures and replaces them with astgen-generated pointers.  e.g.

```
class AstNodeCCall VL_NOT_FINAL : public AstNodeExpr {
    // @astgen op2 := argsp : List[AstNodeExpr]  // ...
    //
    // @astgen ptr := m_funcp : AstCFunc  // <---- ADDED
```

This pull also automates creating brokenGen() to check the pointers, and cloneRelinkGen using this new information, and that allows removing most of the old hand-coded versions.  A new V3Dead stage in development may also use this. At some point I may also auto-generate accessors.

@gezalore, thoughts welcome.
